name: [LoRa] Dense Light / 雲煙 Concept (With multires noise version)
description:
※A LoRa model trained by a friend with multires noise & block weights.

This is a LoRa model that trained by 100+ img generated with NijiV5,and it's the multires noise version.

This model can achieve more detailed the glow and smoke of the campfire in the forest.

weight 1.0 maybe generates better imgs.

forest,outdoors,tree and so on are suggersted tag.
